dct_title_s: Map of the Southern Alps in the Province of Canterbury (New Zealand)
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures. Mountains and major glaciers and rivers are shown. Coast, rivers and lakes coloured blue. From: The Journal of the Royal Geographical Society of London. Vol. 40 (1870), pp. 433-41; held in Firestone Library. Call number: G7 .J687 v. 40 1870.
dct_publisher_sm: London : Published for the Journal of the Royal Geographical Society by J. Murray, 1870.
